sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/ODH Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Operator as Operator Controller<br/>Watch Stream
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet<br/>Node
    participant LlamaPod as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant vLLM as vLLM/Ollama<br/>8000/11434 HTTP
    participant Client as Client Application

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Bearer Token (User)
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>TLS 1.3, Bearer Token (SA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, PVC, SA, RoleBinding<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources Created
    Kubelet->>Registry: Pull Llama Stack Image<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, Registry Credentials
    Registry-->>Kubelet: Image Layers
    Kubelet->>LlamaPod: Start Container
    LlamaPod->>HF: Download Models/Datasets<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, HF Token (optional)
    HF-->>LlamaPod: Model Artifacts
    LlamaPod-->>K8sAPI: Update Status: Ready

    Note over Client,LlamaPod: Flow 2: Inference Request
    Client->>LlamaPod: POST /v1/models/inference<br/>8321/TCP HTTP, No Auth
    LlamaPod->>vLLM: Inference Request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/gRPC, API Key (optional)
    vLLM-->>LlamaPod: Model Response
    LlamaPod-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Prometheus->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.3
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Authorized
    Proxy->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    Operator-->>Proxy: Prometheus Metrics
    Proxy-->>Prometheus: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,LlamaPod: Flow 4: ConfigMap Update
    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap (run.yaml)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>ConfigMap Changed
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment<br/>Trigger Rolling Restart
    K8sAPI->>Kubelet: Create New Pod
    Kubelet->>LlamaPod: Start with New Config
    LlamaPod->>LlamaPod: Load Updated run.yaml
